g.title: j26162231
g.text: Well, now I have the answer to why you're hanging around here so much.

g.title: j463475729
g.text: I suppose I shouldn't have expected you to stay single for long.

g.title: j1815217163
g.text: When you could simply just go back to the future and stay there.

g.title: j1922475774
g.text: I had to follow my heart.

g.title: j2101633171
g.text: Yeah, well. "Sorry" doesn't always cut it.

g.title: j454084028
g.text: I'm glad you finally did. Just wish you had the first time.

g.title: j228023576
g.text: I hope you find happiness this time.

g.title: j172795182
g.text: I know I've left you hanging, while I've tried to sort things out. But given our situation, I think I had every right to take some time.

g.title: j2594502674
g.text: I'm happy for you and Aoi.

g.title: j3463566060
g.text: I suppose I'm surprised, is all.

g.title: j195546541
g.text: I'm happy for you and Eleanor.

g.title: j3289719868
g.text: I figured you didn't have feelings for me in return.

g.title: j2124849841
g.text: Yeah, well, I got sick of waiting.

g.title: j502837221
g.text: You're the one I *really* have feelings for.

g.title: j532344388
g.text: She deserves peace. I hope you can bring her some.

g.title: j38904514
g.text: I'm happy for you and Amir.

g.title: j1621939701
g.text: I know you and Aoi used to be more than friends...

g.title: j2579660951
g.text: I'll do my best not to screw this up.

g.title: j2491694838
g.text: What if I said my relationship was a lie, and I have feelings for you?

g.title: j1489820654
g.text: He could use the confidence having a partner can bring.

g.title: j4055519709
g.text: I'm happy for you and Quincy.

g.title: j2614396109
g.text: So, do you just go about confessing your feelings to everybody and seeing who bites the lure?

g.title: j2611170537
g.text: I know you and Aoi are friends.

g.title: j3079185064
g.text: Deplorable. Stringing someone along like that - someone who trusts you?

g.title: j2473725614
g.text: He needs to learn to let someone in now and then.

g.title: j2106729163
g.text: I'm happy for you and Lettie.

g.title: j3872640790
g.text: But I'm happy for you and Aoi.

g.title: j1544794253
g.text: Sad, maybe. Watching you make her happy in a way I never could.

g.title: j1874883488
g.text: 伙计，我就当帮你个忙，这事我们俩知道就好——希望这只是你又开了黑色幽默的玩笑。

g.title: j684794418
g.text: She needs someone she can share the pain with. Not just physical, either.

g.title: j2120551586
g.text: If any one of us idiots deserve to be happy, it's her.

g.title: j4083151439
g.text: But I'm happy for you and Eleanor.

g.title: j2859548184
g.text: Or are your feelings for Aoi *actually* legitimate?

g.title: j2644152980
g.text: But that's the thing. She's happy when she's with you.

g.title: j2611826338
g.text: If there's one of us knobheads that deserves to be happy, it's her.

g.title: j2707757052
g.text: You can forget about anything ever happening between us. We can stay friends, but that's all it'll be.

g.title: j2907769608
g.text: What if I said my relationship was a lie, and I still had feelings for you?

g.title: j2888204336
g.text: She deserves peace. I hope you can bring her some.

g.title: j4238865941
g.text: But I'm happy for you and Amir.

g.title: j555650378
g.text: Because if any of us deserve to be happy, it's her.

g.title: j2268282637
g.text: Or are your feelings for Eleanor *actually* legitimate?

g.title: j3963246868
g.text: 所以，如果可以的话，请帮我一个忙吧？尽量不要伤害她的心。

g.title: j2668315597
g.text: He could use the confidence having a partner can bring.

g.title: j1975166766
g.text: But I'm happy for you and Quincy.

g.title: j3627638121
g.text: No, it's you I really have feelings for... I just gave up hope.

g.title: j3746102330
g.text: My relationship is real. I promise.

g.title: j2453957469
g.text: Because if you hurt her, I'm not responsible if she decides to scramble your brain.

g.title: j1395168121
g.text: Or are your feelings for Amir *actually* legitimate?

g.title: j532347088
g.text: He needs to learn to let someone in now and then.

g.title: j1880240114
g.text: But I'm happy for you and Lettie.

g.title: j3432171734
g.text: So you're just stringing them along?!

g.title: j4096943894
g.text: I sincerely hope so. For all our sakes.

g.title: j4132199478
g.text: The last thing that man needs is to have his confidence in himself shaken again.

g.title: j944722309
g.text: Or are your feelings for Quincy *actually* legitimate?

g.title: j1602114056
g.text: She needs someone she can share the pain with. Not just physical, either.

g.title: j1615894525
g.text: I mean, I can have feelings for more than one person.

g.title: j990232355
g.text: That man doesn't let people in. You screw that up, it might be the last time he does.

g.title: j4268201546
g.text: Or are your feelings for Lettie *actually* legitimate?

g.title: j3253992993
g.text: Sure, but I can't. And I'm not comfortable with this.

g.title: j1053719652
g.text: Because she hurts enough without you adding onto the pile, mate.
